reviewText: Bought this for my wife.  She said it seemed like the workout didn't do much for her at first because it seemed pretty easy....then she could feel it the next day.  She loves the workout video.

My friend and I meet 3x/week to work out.  We started with Piyo and started dreading our workouts.  I ordered several dvd's from Gunner and we actually look forward to our workouts now-and we're seeing results. Thanks Gunner!!!
Love this dvd great work out
You get a great workout with this video! Its a challenge but its do-able and you'll definitely feel it the next day! I have always been a fan of Core Secrets and love the workout!
